nsent" value="1" required><span>I consent to being contacted about this inquiry and have read the <a href="<?= $url('legal.privacy', [], '/legal/privacy') ?>">Privacy Policy</a>.</span></label><button class="button button-gold">Send inquiry</button></form><aside class="card card-pad stack"><h2 class="heading-card">What happens next</h2><ol class="benefit-list"><li>The inquiry is screened for spam and reviewed privately.</li><li>The Adult Owner reviews commercial terms and any payment arrangement.</li><li>If there is a fit, we discuss scope and a separate written agreement.</li><li>No license, sponsorship, or custom work begins from this form alone.</li></ol><p class="fine-print">Submission time and the privacy-preserving spam result are recorded. Precise location and fingerprinting are not used.</p></aside></div></section>
